Comparison of community-wide, integrated mass drug administration strategies for 
schistosomiasis and soil-transmitted helminthiasis: a cost-effectiveness 
modelling study.

Lo NC(1), Bogoch II(2), Blackburn BG(3), Raso G(4), N'Goran EK(5), Coulibaly 
